creator: Global Hawk
descriptionHtml:
The Global Recharge app is a fast, secure & reliable way to send Airtime or Data bundles credit to friends and families back home.

They can use the credit to make and receive phone calls, surf the web or transfer credit to any other local numbers. The platform is built to make sure all data is processed in a safe and secure way at all times.

The app enables anyone, anywhere to recharge any mobile phone using any operator around the world.
descriptionShort: International Mobile Recharge- Send Airtime & Data Plans in 3 simple steps.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
• Improve performance and app size
• Accept less strict passwords
